snippet.title: Fragment: A Story in Growing | Story Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a stream-of-consciousness life management simulator. As an father, you will burden the weight of life, navigating the successive challenges of your work. With careful planning, balancing income against daily expenses, you'll create a bright and fulfilling life for your dearest family.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2573670/Fragment_A_Story_in_Growing/?beta=0
